title: GET_HELI_TAIL_ROTOR_HEALTH
content:
0xA41BC13D// GetHeliTailRotorHealth
float GET_HELI_TAIL_ROTOR_HEALTH(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The target vehicle.Returns: Return the health of the rear rotor of the helicopter, not the tail rotor.Note: This native is deprecated, please use GET_HELI_REAR_ROTOR_HEALTH instead.
